======CHANGELOG=====

== Version 1.5.1.20100509 ==

- added single.php with conditional tag - individual blog post and portfolio post are styled differently
 - blog posts have more uniform style
- added note on basic install that tells people to set a static home page
- simplified, cleaner CSS
 - removed php in CSS
 - more uniform headline styles
- general code cleanup
- removed auto email on 404, it wasn't working.